						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged in the middle portion. It seems to record an endowment in money, probably 80 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold (?) by <hi rend="bold">Brahma-Śeṭṭi a member of the supervisory committee</hi> of the temple of Tirukkīḻkōṭṭattu-Paramasvāmi at Tirukkuḍamukkil a <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna</hi> in Pāmbūr-nāḍu for feeding two persons daily in the temple after the midday service to the god with special offerings <hi rend="italic">(uttamāgram)</hi></p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
